  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER A PURPOSE</h2>The Last Campfire is an adventure, a story of a lost ember trapped in a puzzling place, searching for meaning and a way home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/7dea646d65e79b1aff773d18bccafa50.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ON A JOURNEY</h2>Travel deeper into the lands beyond the dark forest and overcome the adversities before you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/11463a0221691a53b519bd0adce8d78f.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNCOVER A WORLD</h2>Discover beautiful wilderness filled with lost folk, strange creatures and mysterious ruins.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/15046291b721c294f9a4f4f907880084.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LIGHT THE LAST CAMPFIRE</h2>Find hope and carry it with you on your Journey to light The Last Campfire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/3fcfb9cc29b8e4ec5f8b702ddef118d2.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FROM A SMALL STUDIO</h2>A unique tale from Hello Games and the creative minds behind LostWinds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/44b54f65e0c5066752b851c7900a1657.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER A PURPOSE</h2>The Last Campfire is an adventure, a story of a lost ember trapped in a puzzling place, searching for meaning and a way home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/7dea646d65e79b1aff773d18bccafa50.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ON A JOURNEY</h2>Travel deeper into the lands beyond the dark forest and overcome the adversities before you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/11463a0221691a53b519bd0adce8d78f.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNCOVER A WORLD</h2>Discover beautiful wilderness filled with lost folk, strange creatures and mysterious ruins.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/15046291b721c294f9a4f4f907880084.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LIGHT THE LAST CAMPFIRE</h2>Find hope and carry it with you on your Journey to light The Last Campfire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/3fcfb9cc29b8e4ec5f8b702ddef118d2.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FROM A SMALL STUDIO</h2>A unique tale from Hello Games and the creative minds behind LostWinds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990630/extras/44b54f65e0c5066752b851c7900a1657.avif?t=1725272727\" width=616 height=110 /></span>",
